Package ca.ualberta.cmput301w14t08.geochan.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Comment
    A comment within a thread of comments.
    CommentList
    Container class that stores a comment object, its id, and a list of children commentLists that match the Comment's child replies.
    CustomMarker
    Custom Marker class designed to construct map Marker objects and handle their operations.
    ElasticSearchCountResponse
    Represents a count response served by ElasticSearch.
    ElasticSearchDocs<T>
    A multi-document query on ElasticSearch.
    ElasticSearchHits<T>
    Represents a hit within a response served by ElasticSearch.
    ElasticSearchResponse<T>
    Represents a response served by ElasticSearch.
    ElasticSearchSearchResponse<T>
    Represents a search response served by ElasticSearch.
    FavouritesLog
    Handles the threads/comments saved by the user as favourite, to be available for later viewing.
    GeoLocation
    Responsible for GeoLocation services for Comment objects Responsible for keeping track of location, latitude and longitude values, point of interest string (location description), and calculating distance between itself and another geoLocation object.
    GeoLocationLog
    Handles all operations involved in logging used locations.
    ThreadComment
    Handles all operations of threads in the application.
    ThreadList
    Stores and manages an ArrayList of ThreadComment objects.
